'''Grant Raymond George''' ([[19 May|May 19]], [[1971]]) is an American voice actor. He played [[Legolas|Legolas Greenleaf]] and Troll Stonehurler in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: War of the Ring]]''.

==Roles==
* [[2004]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: War of the Ring]]'': [[Legolas|Legolas Greenleaf]], Troll Stonehurler
